title: Intervention S11E05 - Larry and Megan
description:
Although Season 11 isn't hard to find, I add this episode for two reasons: 1) the ridiculousness of Larry, an alcoholic in severe denial; and 2) Megan recently passed away, but she was beautiful, intelligent, and a heroin user. With her heroin use partially sparked by her intellectual curiosity, I hope that she was able to complete her masters before she passed.
Intervention, Season 11, Episode 5.
